data.description: This like new 3/2 boasts a new roof, HVAC and privacy fence. You will find hardwood and tile throughout with a large living space that opens up to a nice screened in porch. The master has a double vanity and a large walk in closet. The bedrooms are generous in size and all the windows have 2 inch blinds. The kitchen has a pantry and offers a lot of natural light. You will want to see this one in person to see how clean and ready it is for you to call home.
